  "title": "Death Sound",
  "description": "Plays a sound to all players when someone dies! (17-23 sounds + their variants)",
  "body": "# DeathSound\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/El-Kavio/DeathSound/assets/140896938/2bcd8e82-de53-4162-93c9-1f0cc6aa8959\" alt=\"DeathSound banner\" width=\"50%\">\n\n---\n\n**DeathSound** is a **datapack** that plays a **sound** to all players whenever one of them dies.<br>\nThere are <abbr title=\"Depends on the version you're using (updated from latest releases of each version).\">17-23 sounds</abbr> and their **variants**, selected to add a more fearsome experience to yours and others deaths.\n\n<details><summary>Example video</summary>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZqsjF_wGKBY\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</details>\n\n## How to update\n\nSimply **delete** the **DeathSound** folder and **replace** it with the **new** one!\n\n---\n\n[![ko-fi](https://ko-fi.com/img/githubbutton_sm.svg)](https://ko-fi.com/kavio)\n",
